title.narrative: Enhanced Nutrition, Stepping Up Resilience and Enterprise (ENSURE)

description.narrative: (Zimbabwe): The ENSURE Program addresses food and nutrition insecurity through establishment of community assets, diversified crop and livestock production, and promotion of positive health and nutrition behaviors. The program reaches vulnerable households in arid and semi-arid areas...With FY 2019 funds, ENSURE will:.Improve farming techniques and management practices to increase production and respond to climatic shocks;Establish community assets for increased production of safe, nutritious foods ;Link smallholder farmers with financial institutions, buyers and input suppliers;Promote micro and small enterprises to diversify livelihoods options for purchase of food year round and reduce financial risks;Provide supplementary food to children under two and pregnant and lactating women to reduce stunting;Promote positive nutrition and hygiene behaviors to reduce child chronic malnutrition; andDevelop community disaster risk reduction and early warning systems to mitigate shocks.. ..... .. ... .
